WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 20=
=If You Forget Love=

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.240
Do you still remember that story?

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:21.960
The guy's name was Aming.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:24.200
The girl's name was Ding Daang.

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:26.720
They were deeply in love.

00:01:27.440 --> 00:01:28.360
But later on,

00:01:29.160 --> 00:01:30.240
they separated.

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.720
I want to rewrite that ending.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.880
So this was all part of your plan?

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:40.360
Yes.

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:50.920
Why would you do that?

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:52.960
Because I love you.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:57.040
Because I can't let go of what we had.

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:09.560
Aming,

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:13.280
everyone's waiting for you to come back.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.720
What if I can tell
if my memories are real or not?

00:02:20.720 --> 00:02:21.880
That's okay.

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:25.560
As long as you know
whether love is real.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:27.280
That's enough.

00:02:28.120 --> 00:02:28.960
Ding Daang.

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:34.160
If I lose everything,

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:36.960
if I hit rock bottom,

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:39.960
would you still want me?

00:02:41.880 --> 00:02:42.800
Aming.

00:02:44.400 --> 00:02:45.560
I told you before,

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:49.560
we don't need a perfect score every time.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.040
For me,

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:01.400
you're never a loser.

00:03:11.700 --> 00:03:15.220
(One year ago)

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:24.360
Ding Daang.

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:27.560
Do you remember me?

00:03:33.240 --> 00:03:34.240
I'm Miaomiao.

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:36.360
Miaomiao.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:39.960
What brings you here?

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:41.880
Ding Daang,

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:44.440
my brother is dying.

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:47.360
What did you say?

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:49.920
What happened to Aming?

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:51.920
It's not his body.

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:53.640
It's his mind.

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:56.160
He's not himself anymore.

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:57.560
Please, save him.

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.200
After my brother went abroad,

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:05.680
he's been living in constant pain.

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:07.200
That's why he founded Keep Love.

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:10.200
(Suga Love)
It was meant to shield users from pain,

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:11.600
keeping only their happy memories.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.120
But in the end,

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.280
the experiment failed.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:19.200
He developed a severe bipolar disorder,

00:04:19.200 --> 00:04:20.400
along with schizophrenia,

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:22.120
and changed his name to Yu Kun.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:24.520
Ding Daang,

00:04:24.840 --> 00:04:25.680
please help me

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.080
save my brother.

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.360
What can I do?

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:33.040
My boyfriend, Hu Yitong,

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:34.560
is an exceptional psychologist.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.000
When I was completely lost,

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:38.680
he's the one who healed me.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.320
He said,

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:42.040
my brother has relied on med to suppress

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:43.540
Chen Aming's personality for too long.

00:04:43.540 --> 00:04:45.680
Normal treatments hardly work anymore.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:47.580
My brother needs to face his memories

00:04:47.580 --> 00:04:48.680
as Chen Aming and Yu Kun

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.520
and rebuid his perception

00:04:50.520 --> 00:04:52.080
through reliving the past.

00:04:52.640 --> 00:04:53.480
That way,

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:55.000
the recovery rate

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.440
could reach ninety percent.

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:00.320
But the process
will be incredibly painful.

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:03.160
It's like tearing open a healed scar

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.240
and feeling the wound again.

00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:13.100
But we haven't seen each other for years.

00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:15.520
How can you be sure

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:16.800
that I can really help him?

00:05:18.760 --> 00:05:20.800
Because 90% of his most painful memories

00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:24.000
is about you.

00:05:38.280 --> 00:05:39.360
We've been at it all night.

00:05:40.200 --> 00:05:41.480
Get some sleep, okay?

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:52.920
Ding Daang.

00:06:01.640 --> 00:06:02.480
I'm thinking of

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.600
calling Keep Love quits.

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:12.320
Alright.

00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:19.000
Aren't you gonna ask why?

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:22.720
No need to ask.

00:06:28.040 --> 00:06:28.880
Aming.

00:06:31.920 --> 00:06:32.840
No matter what happens,

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:35.520
I'll be right here with you.

00:06:50.260 --> 00:06:52.140
(Three months ago)

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:53.380
The Tong Sui store in Aiye Town

00:06:53.380 --> 00:06:55.160
is where Aming and I first met.

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:57.080
I've already bought the place.

00:06:57.960 --> 00:06:59.240
The initial plan's done.

00:06:59.880 --> 00:07:01.280
Now we move to the next step.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:02.840
Miaomiao,

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:04.480
you keep playing the role

00:07:04.480 --> 00:07:06.640
of that poor soul heartbroken by Dr. Hu.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:08.640
Dr. Hu.

00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:11.680
I'll need your help

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:13.000
to pretend to be my fiancé.

00:07:15.400 --> 00:07:17.400
Do you really think this will work?

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:20.280
Of course not, not like this.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:22.000
So,

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.480
I want to bring Liu Xiaoting back.

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:27.000
Ding Daang,

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.480
why are you looking for her?

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:34.760
Liu Xiaoting is the key piece

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.880
in this plan.

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:38.760
She can also help you

00:07:38.760 --> 00:07:39.760
let go of the past.

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.200
I believe in you.

00:07:44.640 --> 00:07:46.240
So that means

00:07:46.440 --> 00:07:48.120
we need to involve different people

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:50.160
to make Boss face

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:51.400
the memories of the past.

00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:52.880
Regular medication

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:54.640
can no longer slow down the illness.

00:07:54.640 --> 00:07:56.360
This is the only way left.

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:58.000
But it's going to be tough on Xibei

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:58.960
and Haoran.

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:00.760
You'll have to monitor his data in real time

00:08:00.760 --> 00:08:02.080
in case anything going wrong.

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:03.640
Xibei,

00:08:03.640 --> 00:08:04.480
Haoran,

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:05.480
from here on,

00:08:05.960 --> 00:08:07.260
it's up to you two to guide him.

00:08:08.400 --> 00:08:09.960
I'll step in when the moment comes

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:11.400
to give him a strong mental jolt.

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:14.920
This time we'll push harder than ever.

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:16.800
Bit by bit,

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:17.640
step by step,

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:19.020
we'll drag him out

00:08:19.020 --> 00:08:20.360
from that cold prison of data.

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:22.720
We'll answer pain with pain,

00:08:23.880 --> 00:08:25.360
fight oblivion with memory,

00:08:27.380 --> 00:08:28.690
and spark a love as sweet as sugar

00:08:31.200 --> 00:08:32.720
from the illusion of hate.

00:09:02.120 --> 00:09:03.920
Thank you for never giving up on Aming.

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:16.920
Thank you.

00:09:16.920 --> 00:09:17.760
Ding Daang.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.800
Let's bring Chen Aming back together.

00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:47.160
You just started dating

00:09:47.160 --> 00:09:49.040
and you're already bossing her around?

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:50.440
Do you pay her for this?

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:52.100
Xibei,

00:09:52.100 --> 00:09:53.290
thinking about switching jobs?

00:09:54.720 --> 00:09:56.400
Ah, that sweet love story…

00:09:56.400 --> 00:09:58.800
Finally, it's Feifei's turn.

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:00.840
Looks like our bar's got some good vibes.

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:02.560
Our?

00:10:06.240 --> 00:10:07.280
You guys finally made it!

00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:09.520
Later, we'll raise a glass
to you, Dr. Hu.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.040
No.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.400
A toast to Mr. Steven.

00:10:14.040 --> 00:10:15.080
Steven's not me.

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:17.280
It's Ding Daang.

00:10:20.700 --> 00:10:21.560
Ding Daang

00:10:21.560 --> 00:10:22.520
is the most perfer woman

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.000
I've ever met.

00:10:25.520 --> 00:10:26.640
You have no idea.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:29.200
When the Ding Family went bankrupt,

00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:30.400
I went looking for her.

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:33.440
She was alone in that huge, empty house,

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:35.940
too scared to even turn on the lights.

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:38.520
I knew you were in there.

00:10:38.800 --> 00:10:40.080
Ding Haishan's daughter.

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:41.600
Your father is gone for good,

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.280
but the debts still need to be paid.

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:44.760
Open the door!

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:46.000
He owed twenty million.

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:47.040
You can't get away.

00:10:47.480 --> 00:10:48.680
Stop hiding.

00:10:48.680 --> 00:10:49.680
Come out!

00:10:50.280 --> 00:10:51.520
Hurry up and come out!

00:10:51.520 --> 00:10:52.720
I know you're inside!

00:10:59.320 --> 00:11:00.320
Gentlemen,

00:11:00.920 --> 00:11:02.040
I'll repay my fathers debts.

00:11:03.160 --> 00:11:04.040
I promise.

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:05.600
As long as I'm alive,

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:06.760
this debt won't go unpaid.

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:15.000
Luckily,

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:16.840
she's got a sharp eye

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:19.240
and seized the chance in e-commerce.

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:21.000
No money,

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.000
no connections,

00:11:22.920 --> 00:11:25.400
just pure determination not to give up.

00:11:25.400 --> 00:11:26.720
She built Meiman into

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:29.520
a live streaming platform
with 170 million users.

00:11:29.520 --> 00:11:32.320
Its annual transaction volume
exceeds ten billion.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.300
Let's move it ourselves.

00:11:33.300 --> 00:11:34.720
We'll save dozens of bucks.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:36.040
Consider it a workout.

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:39.040
Do you think heaven,

00:11:39.160 --> 00:11:40.680
seeing us work so hard,

00:11:41.040 --> 00:11:42.800
will make us rich someday?

00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:47.240
It definitely will.

00:11:48.640 --> 00:11:49.490
Come on, let's go.

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:50.560
Keep going.

00:11:54.520 --> 00:11:55.960
She didn't just save herself.

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:58.120
She also saved the ones she loved.

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:02.600
But what Ding Daang didn't know was

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:04.600
the choice Aming made back then

00:12:05.240 --> 00:12:06.920
was also something he couldn't control.

00:12:08.800 --> 00:12:10.240
Keep Love's original purpose

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:12.880
was to help people
enhance their sense of joy.

00:12:13.480 --> 00:12:14.320
Boss.

00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:15.960
It's still in the testing stage.

00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:17.320
It could be dangerous.

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:18.860
Are you sure about doing this?

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:20.720
Precisely because of that,

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:21.880
I have to do it myself.

00:12:22.840 --> 00:12:24.400
This is software bug testing.

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:25.360
It's to protect users

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:26.800
and ensure complete data security.

00:12:28.360 --> 00:12:29.560
What if something goes wrong?

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:31.480
How could anything go wrong?

00:12:32.680 --> 00:12:34.680
No one knows Keep Love better than I do.

00:12:35.080 --> 00:12:36.600
No one could've done it better than me.

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:37.680
But I knew that

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:40.600
Aming only did it to erase his pain.

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:45.280
The best algorithm

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:48.280
is to test it on yourself

00:12:50.680 --> 00:12:51.640
Unfortunately,

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:52.760
the experiment failed.

00:12:53.230 --> 00:12:54.080
He turned into Yu Kun,

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:56.600
who was like a cold, precise machine.

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:58.440
What's worse,

00:12:58.840 --> 00:13:00.640
Yu Kun is unpredictable.

00:13:01.160 --> 00:13:02.960
He could hurt himself at any time.

00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:18.640
Thank you, everyone.

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:20.680
Really.

00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:24.200
Thank you for helping me
find my brother.

00:13:33.160 --> 00:13:34.400
Now, Yu Kun's

00:13:34.400 --> 00:13:36.000
post‑traumatic dissociative response

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:37.040
is slowly easing.

00:13:37.900 --> 00:13:38.990
His personality integration

00:13:39.640 --> 00:13:40.640
has made great progress.

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:43.380
His recovery is going well.

00:13:43.380 --> 00:13:45.360
Credit goes to our psychologist, Dr. Hu.

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:46.720
If I get traumatized,

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:47.560
I'm coming to you.

00:13:47.560 --> 00:13:48.800
What are you thinking about?

00:13:49.080 --> 00:13:50.320
When you're with me,

00:13:50.320 --> 00:13:51.680
there's only sweetness,

00:13:51.680 --> 00:13:52.640
no trauma at all.

00:13:54.280 --> 00:13:55.680
Being an actor

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:57.680
is way tougher than being a doctor.

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:00.000
To be honest,

00:14:00.640 --> 00:14:01.760
some scenes

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:03.280
really do come off a bit awkward.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:06.400
But I've got to say,
Dr. Hu is truly dedicated.

00:14:06.400 --> 00:14:07.960
Whether Yu Kun's around or not,

00:14:07.960 --> 00:14:09.400
he still performs like it's real.

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:11.600
But it's not time to relax yet.

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:13.640
That guy's mind

00:14:13.640 --> 00:14:14.680
is still a total mess.

00:14:16.640 --> 00:14:17.760
But at least...

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:19.760
But at least,

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:22.600
my brother's started

00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:24.440
acting like himself again,

00:14:25.280 --> 00:14:26.120
hasn't he?

00:14:35.200 --> 00:14:36.600
We've all been putting on a show,

00:14:37.680 --> 00:14:39.320
but she did all this for you,

00:14:40.080 --> 00:14:42.160
to help you heal.

00:14:43.040 --> 00:14:44.400
That's why she brought you back

00:14:44.920 --> 00:14:46.920
to trigger Chen Aming's memories

00:14:48.800 --> 00:14:50.160
and make Yu Kun fade away?

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:52.680
She wanted your existence to feel whole.

00:14:52.920 --> 00:14:54.400
Ding Daang said, whether you're Yu Kun

00:14:54.400 --> 00:14:55.240
or Chen Aming,

00:14:55.400 --> 00:14:56.920
you have to face the past

00:14:56.920 --> 00:14:58.360
to have a future.

00:14:59.080 --> 00:14:59.920
Ding Daang,

00:15:00.560 --> 00:15:01.760
you said you wanted forever.

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:04.840
I promise you.

00:15:32.140 --> 00:15:39.140
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:15:43.540 --> 00:15:50.900
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:15:55.350 --> 00:15:57.290
♪They say♪

00:15:57.700 --> 00:16:06.080
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:09.580
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:15.750
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:16:17.130 --> 00:16:22.890
♪I've already lost you♪

00:16:22.890 --> 00:16:28.370
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:16:28.670 --> 00:16:34.620
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:16:34.620 --> 00:16:39.400
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:16:40.510 --> 00:16:44.540
♪The past will always pass♪

00:16:44.870 --> 00:16:52.450
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:16:52.920 --> 00:16:56.170
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:16:56.730 --> 00:17:02.380
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:17:04.840 --> 00:17:08.370
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:17:08.370 --> 00:17:14.630
♪But sadly, it's not you♪